OL,3,CShop price increases ease amid hopes
OL,4,Cof Christmas boost to consumer
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,FBlack Friday drove an easing of shop
OL,8,Fprice increases in November amid hopes
OL,9,Fthat consumer confidence will rebound
OL,10,Fin the final weeks before Christmas.
OL,12,FOverall shop prices were 0.6% higher
OL,13,Fthan a year ago last month, down from
OL,14,F1% in October, according to the
OL,15,FBritish Retail Consortium (BRC) and
OL,16,Fmarket researchers NIQ.
