OL,7,FFood inflation also slowed, to 3% from
OL,8,FOctober's 3.7%, as widespread
OL,9,Fpromotions meant price rises eased
OL,10,Fespecially in dairy, fruit, bread and
OL,11,Fcereals.
OL,13,FHowever, inflation remained stubbornly
OL,14,Fhigh for oils and fats as well as meat
OL,15,Fand fish.
OL,17,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,18,Fsaid: "Black Friday deals began
OL,19,Fearlier than normal as competition
OL,20,Fbetween retailers hit fever pitch.
