OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,FHowever, Ms Dickinson warned:
OL,8,F"Headwinds in the new year include
OL,9,Frising employment costs which are
OL,10,Flikely to filter through to prices.
OL,11,FThis could shake already weak consumer
OL,12,Fconfidence and present further
OL,13,Fchallenges for consumers in the year
OL,14,Fahead."
OL,16,FMike Watkins, head of retailer and
OL,17,Fbusiness insight at NIQ, said: "It's
OL,18,Fgood news for shoppers that price
OL,19,Fincreases are slowing but inflationary
OL,20,Fpressures still remain, in particular
OL,21,Fwithin food.
